{"tid":2017339,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控方播片 揭警影市民記者大頭","createTime":"2020-05-15T04:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T14:18:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e84ca3051bbfe2e12b1492e6180f2193a7bbcf5f","tid":2017339,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200515/UVTP4RMNS7CJCO5ZOVRVZOZ4F4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FUVTP4RMNS7CJCO5ZOVRVZOZ4F4%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRbidffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=491ca72f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FUVTP4RMNS7CJCO5ZOVRVZOZ4F4%2F&h=07a7a514\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200515/UVTP4RMNS7CJCO5ZOVRVZOZ4F4/</a><br />\n<br />\n控方播片 揭警影市民記者大頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200515/large/1589475011_1ce0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200515%2Flarge%2F1589475011_1ce0.jpg&h=bddb6b02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告杜依蘭（左）及湯偉雄昨手牽手應訊。張志華攝<br />\n<br />\n【赴湯杜火案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年7月28日上環嚴重警民衝突，湯氏夫婦與少女被控暴動罪。案件昨續審，當日負責呼籲示威者散去。。。。。。。。。。。。。。郭家麒、香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒及成員周庭的容貌，亦遭放大聚焦。<br />\n<br />\n被告依次為夫婦湯偉雄（39歲）與杜依蘭（42歲），以及17歲姓李。。。。。。。。。。。。湯杜二人另被控無牌管有無線電對講機罪。<br />\n<br />\n控方昨播放多條現場影片，辯方不滿部份片段的案發時間重叠。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。場情況，「有好多人可能會作出不必要嘅講法」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n督察作供屢稱「相信係」<br />\n<br />\n吳智偉看影片時指出，示威者當日曾作出叫囂、向警方掟雜物、用膠水馬築防線。。。。。。。。。。。。。肯定地上物件是磚頭，吳稱「非常肯定」，當郭官再問他是否肯定飛擲於空中的物品是甚麼時，吳則指「頗肯定」。<br />\n<br />\n吳智偉昨跟前日一樣，散庭後「走後門」離開大樓，雖然仍有。。。。。。。。。。。機構前日指出，停車場及地下範圍也不屬法院。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC872/19<br />\n■記者劉偉琪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200515/large/1589475010_68ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200515%2Flarge%2F1589475010_68ee.jpg&h=15442719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n督察吳智偉"},{"pid":"a360b621dbfaa51707669132dacf7db0982d656b","tid":2017339,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294c2f3b6983b478a100e98642f6ffda571e2153","tid":2017339,"uid":100581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:06:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提提你：蘋果有部分新聞，唔駛俾錢都可以入去睇到，click入去幫手提高佢地個點擊率。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9147edb47149a5239d042277d2c9c5eb9157b0b3","tid":2017339,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"佢地當時係立法會議員助理"}]}